<div class="content-panel standalone content-row">
<div style="padding: 5px 15px;">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><em>So, the SCP Foundation is quickly becoming, if it is not already, a &quot;thing&quot; on the internets. However, there is one more step we must take before we become a full-out &quot;thing.&quot;</em></p>
<p><em>Terrible crossover fanfiction.</em></p>
<p><em>This is your challenge: write a crossover fanfiction between the SCP Foundation and any other fictional universe of your choice. It can be hilarious, tongue-in-cheek, or deadly serious, just as long as it is well-written. Extra points scored for &quot;crackiest&quot; crossover.</em></p>
<p><em>That is all.</em><br />
<em>~Clef</em></p>
